snippet.title: The World Begins With You // Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
After being asleep for a long time, you wake up in an old prison cell. You turn around, what was that? 

Soon after, you are free, unexpectedly.

You reach daylight and enter a beautiful, long forgotten and sometimes dangerous world.

What awaits you at the end of your journey?

===========

The World Begins With You is a short indie game created during the Wizard Jam 6 gamejam in late December 2017.

It can be downloaded for free here:
https://fabiandenter.itch.io/the-world-begins-with-you

Follow me on twitter:
https://twitter.com/fabiandenter
